name: Affirm It
description:
The System is rigged in Your favour.
The sham is nothing but a Show.
The list is written with Your name at the top of the Order.
The Gifts are handed down with You first in row.

Look under the tree.
Check behind Your chair.
Turn the page to see what You've begun.
I don't think You'll quite actually Believe it.
But look, You've already Won.
